org.hl7.xml.parser
Class MessageElementContentHandler

java.lang.Object
  org.hl7.xml.parser.DynamicContentHandlerBase
      org.hl7.xml.parser.MessageElementContentHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
DynamicContentHandler, DynamicContentHandler.ResultReceiver, org.xml.sax.ContentHandler
public class MessageElementContentHandler
extends DynamicContentHandlerBase
implements DynamicContentHandler, DynamicContentHandler.ResultReceiver

An XML SAX content handler for parsing generic HL7 message elements that stem from RIM class clones.

If you need an introduction into SAX parser design, see the appendix after the Java code in this file.

Also note the DynamicContentHandler interface which adds significant magic to the functioning of this code.
